items.title: Search for suspects in shooting that left 4 dead, 12 wounded in Mississippi
items.description: Officials in Leland, Mississippi, are calling on the public's help after four people were killed and 12 others wounded in a mass shooting.

items.title: Oscar-winning actress Diane Keaton dies at 79
items.description: Diane Keaton, the Oscar-winning actress known for her performances in "Annie Hall" and "The Godfather," has died at the age of 79.
